data.description: You must see my amazing new listing in Covington, GA,  that's very close to expressways and shopping. It's less than 30 minutes to the city of Atlanta. The huge master suite has a large designated sitting room for private lounging, with huge closets, a sexy spa bathroom, with double vanities and convenient access to the laundry room. You will fall in love with the amazing Chefs kitchen, that has double ovens, built in microwave, gas cooktop and an oversized island wide enough to hold large Holiday dinner buffets, plus seating for 4-5 around it. You also get a bonus having an oversized pantry closet and a butlers pantry for more serving and storage space. Now let's talk about the bedroom on the main, which is so perfect for the in-laws or someone that has mobility issues, as the owners have converted the tub/shower into a walk-in shower for handicap access. All secondary bedrooms have private bathroom entries and large closets. This home is much larger than it looks, being close to 4,000 sq. ft.. Let me also mention that the property has a nice size leveled fenced-in yard. There's so much more to tell.
